tion based on the\nproposed method. One of the findings in this study is that the channel models\nof the operating environment and the performance of the channel estimation\nmethod must be considered during RIS design to exploit performance improvement\nas far as possible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 19:15:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Jan 2022 19:50:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 12 May 2022 20:01:28 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 23 Jul 2022 10:21:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-26"}
