rge number of nanoparticle catalysts. This technique will\nenable the identification of catalytically functional surface structures and\nstrengthen our ability to establish (dynamic) structure-activity relationships.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Apr 2021 00:13:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-05"}
